game.description:
The two popular Disney Frozen princesses have come together to join the wonderful Royals Rock band. An awesome show has been organized by them in the evening. Almost everything is ready except her dressing style. Would you help them to pick up the nice outfit for this mega event? Join Elsa And Anna Royals Rock Dress game and be prepared to design an awesome combination of dresses combined with a matching hairstyle and a pair of matching shoes!
It is common for these two Disney princesses to try different dress styles on different occasion. But, they now need your help to pick up some royal rock outfits in this brand new dressing game for girls. Choose your princess and browse her huge dress collection to get a perfect stage look! A new edgy hairstyle and a pink and silver glittery gown can help Elsa look fabulous. You can also select a long top with star prints and combine it with a pair of lovely, matching blue sparking leggings. 
Give your favorite princess a blue color tiara on her head and complete her look with a pink color guitar in this html5 dress up game! Next move to Anna who loves to wear a unique orange color hairstyle with two quirky ponytail-burns! Give her an asymmetric ruffled outfit available in multiple colors and a glamorous pink color dress! A pink color tiara will suit her the most. Also give her the needful microphone to make her the lead singer! All the best to enjoy a lot in our free girls mobile games, no download required!
